File Structure
nutrition_tracker/        //Main project folder
│── nutrition_tracker.py   //Main entry point (runs the whole program)
│── data/                  //Stores user accounts, logs, and tracking data
│   │── users/               //Stores individual user data files
│   │── logs/                //Stores log files for debugging
│── modules/               //Organized feature modules
│   │── user_management/     //Handles user login, signup, and data
│   │   │── auth.py            //Manages login/signup & authentication
│   │   │── user_data.py       // Handles user-specific data storage
│   │── tracking/            // Manages daily tracking of nutrition
│   │   │── calorie_tracker.py  //Tracks daily calorie intake
│   │   │── protein_tracker.py  //Tracks daily protein intake
│   │   │── future_macros.py    //Placeholder for carbs, fats, etc.
│   │── goals/               //Handles goal setting & selection
│   │   │── goal_selection.py   // User goal selection (gain/lose)
│   │   │── goal_management.py  //Handles goal changes & calculations
│   │── summaries/           //Handles weekly, monthly, and daily summaries
│   │   │── daily_summary.py    //Displays daily tracking data
│   │   │── weekly_summary.py   //Generates weekly reports
│   │   │── monthly_summary.py  //Generates monthly reports
